  "usageNotes": [
    "Use soccer-learning for tiered educational cards and contextual match explainer inserts.",
    "Use world-cup-fun-facts for lightweight promotional or filler content where live data is unavailable.",
    "Use soccer-learning-sources to show provenance and decide which cards need scheduled review.",
    "Use world-cup-guide-page to drive the standalone page without hard-coding section order in the UI.",
    "Use famous-absences with explicit labels and dates so the page never implies a player is simply missing without explanation.",
    "Use soccer-glossary plus the page's global search to create a practical dictionary without needing accounts or personalization.",
    "Use fan-culture-atlas to make team discovery feel human, not just tactical.",
    "Use var-offside-lab to explain offside and VAR visually before fans hit the rule explainers in prose."
